OL,5, Major high street fashion brands have  
OL,6, paid factories in Bangladesh less than 
OL,7, the cost of producing their clothes,   
OL,8, researchers claim.                     
OL,10,FA survey of 1,000 factories found many 
OL,11,Fwere paid the same prices as before the
OL,12,Fpandemic two years ago - despite       
OL,13,Fsoaring costs of materials.            
OL,15,FOne in five said they struggled to pay 
OL,16,FBangladesh's #2.30 a day minimum wage. 
OL,18,FAberdeen University's Business School  
OL,19,Fcarried out the research alongside     
OL,20,Fjustice charity Transform Trade.       
